data.description: Country living at its best with lots of space. This 4 bedroom 2 bath house is sitting on 1.27 acres in Prairiland school district. There is a 30X30 insulated shop. Enjoy the outdoors with a stocked pond and a covered 30x12 back patio. The A/C and roof are both 5 years old.  The Stove and fridge do not convey with the property.
